  <num>42-408</num>
  <heading>Record of conveyance by infant or infant trustee as evidence.</heading>
  <text>The record or a copy thereof of any deed recorded shall be evidence thereof, in the same manner and shall have the same effect as if such deed had been originally executed, acknowledged, and recorded according to law.</text>
